To Build:
mvn clean install

To Run:
mvn exec:java -Dexec.mainClass="com.apple.merchant.PaymentDecryptHelper"

To Run With Arguments:
mvn exec:java -Dexec.mainClass="com.apple.merchant.PaymentDecryptHelper"
-DpublicCertificate=X
-Ddata=""
